Overview

Theme: This place is full of people who are having a difficult time in society

It should feel somber.

You should hear the crackling of fire cans, hear people talking, laughing, crying, shouting, and more.

between two support beems you can see the hanging of peoples uniforms to dry and be ready for them tomorrow. Roughly 40 - 60% of homeless camps in seattle have part-time and full-time jobs.
